WEBVTT

00:09.853 --> 00:13.689
We need more water!

00:13.723 --> 00:15.557
- Hill, Flynn, Grant!
- Yes, sir?

00:15.592 --> 00:17.626
We got to get this under control.

00:17.660 --> 00:20.796
We got old, combustible
buildings in a tight space.

00:20.830 --> 00:22.598
Grant, you're with Hill.

00:22.632 --> 00:24.133
Where do you want us, chief?

00:24.167 --> 00:25.734
I need you guys to spread out inside.

00:25.769 --> 00:27.939
Knock it down as much
as you can, okay? Now, go!

00:29.239 --> 00:30.406
All right, listen,
I'll take the rear.

00:30.440 --> 00:32.307
- I got the roof.
- I'll take the front.

00:32.342 --> 00:34.843
Let's all go home.

00:40.850 --> 00:43.719
Let's go! Let's go!

